{
  "stem": "20609.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was run by the Jews and you-- we had our Jewish elder council, you know, where matter of fact, Rabbi Beck from Berlin was on the elders council and the Jewish elders, his name was Epstein.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was the head of the Jewish community in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one of the things we had was every so often, maybe once or twice or three times a month, transports were going east and this was for labor purposes.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then you started seeing the people in-- in-- in crutches, you know, like we had-- Theresienstadt initially was considered a prominent camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had Jewish war veterans from the First World War there, they had blind people-- all veterans, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the beginning, they were sort of exempt from transport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then things changed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All of a sudden, they clean out the camp, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we also get a new commandant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like the beginning of '44 we get a new commandant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And by the way, the old commandant only recently died in Frankfurt at the age of 82.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I can't think of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know what the-- the other commandant, his name was Ron.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I-- I think I even have the article about it and it's-- the headline used to say, if you want to hide and you're a war criminal, live in Germany.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This guy died in a hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was wanted by every government-- Russia, France, Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, Germany, too, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this guy died under his real name in a Frankfurt hospital at the age of 82.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Go ahead, figure that one out, right?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now we get a new commandant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All of a sudden, I get a new assignment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a heavenly assignment.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
